    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组队协作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回家的路崎岖难行，挑战重重。和伙伴们一起推动、操控购物车，清理前方道路。引开那些想抢走你们东西的动物（还有人类！）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/920cff2943ae756a569091ec9e8dcfe8.poster.avif?t=1772474955\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/920cff2943ae756a569091ec9e8dcfe8.webm?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/920cff2943ae756a569091ec9e8dcfe8.mp4?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>运用你的浣熊物理学位</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用弹力绳、木板等各种道具，驱动你的购物车从障碍物上方越过、下方钻过，或是从中穿行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/dda472a42274efd6c88597d42898790e.poster.avif?t=1772474955\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/dda472a42274efd6c88597d42898790e.webm?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/dda472a42274efd6c88597d42898790e.mp4?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>搜刮整个世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打翻垃圾桶、翻找大型垃圾箱、搜遍荒野，寻找有用的物品和值钱的废品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/373ef74402630245c3f62b33a7becd44.poster.avif?t=1772474955\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/373ef74402630245c3f62b33a7becd44.webm?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/373ef74402630245c3f62b33a7becd44.mp4?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>体验最棒的浣熊生活</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界中攀爬、乱窜、四处蹦跳。和朋友玩拍手游戏。随手吃点垃圾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/e46d1ddb26ea207178640ec18d4c69ca.poster.avif?t=1772474955\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/e46d1ddb26ea207178640ec18d4c69ca.webm?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314580/extras/e46d1ddb26ea207178640ec18d4c69ca.mp4?t=1772474955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
